    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> The thing is since have a generic code for facets I do not want to have a separate template\n\nFirst you will not be able to have a single template for refinement list and hierarchical facet because on one side you want checkboxes while you want menu on the other.\n\nthe current magento demo with instantsearch.js is using checkboxes for hierarchical facet and it looks weird of course.\n\nLet's wait until you have the hierarchical menu with some good style, only missing what you need here and then we see how to solve it.\n\nPing me when it's ok.\n",
