    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, but you can also use specific styling on the third level with `.ais-hierarchical-menu--list .ais-hierarchical-menu--list .ais-hierarchical-menu--list`. You would rarely have more than three levels, and this issue was about distinguishing between first level and others.\n",
